Therefore,

00:20:48.400 --> 00:20:49.460
I need to find an

00:20:50.200 --> 00:20:53.180
outstanding male immortal with

00:20:53.880 --> 00:20:56.150
excellent character, extraordinary appearance

00:20:56.150 --> 00:20:57.640
who unconditionally supports me

00:20:57.640 --> 00:20:59.220
in nurturing the Water Gelling Beasts,

00:20:59.510 --> 00:21:00.870
