Let me go!

00:23:48.400 --> 00:23:49.420
I don't need you.

00:24:00.830 --> 00:24:01.790
I've come so many times to

00:24:01.790 --> 00:24:03.220
this dense forest of the Forbidden Valley.

00:24:03.750 --> 00:24:05.900
If the Fire Phoenix immortal spirit were here,

00:24:06.200 --> 00:24:07.350
I would have found it long ago.

00:24:08.030 --> 00:24:09.420
Why bother coming here?

00:24:10.720 --> 00:24:12.070
Maybe we'll find it.

00:24:14.400 --> 00:24:15.940
I don't think so.

